The FIDE World Youth Chess Olympiad 2017 organized by Gujarat State Chess Association will take place in Ahmedabad, INDIA from December 10th to December 19th.
Each FIDE member country has the right to send one team of 5 players and 1 captain with free board and lodging.

Rameshbabu Praggnanandhaa vs Alireza Firouzja
